name: Dominic
description: [Human | Fighter] 'Dracul Bond' Passive: If Avatar Dracul is equipped, Dominic Gains +25 ATK. Additionally, Upon death Dominic returns to the field at the start of your next Standby Phase with 75% of his HP. This effect occurs once.
